MESSAGE: Oh it's nothing! Now, today's question: What is your favourite food?
Welcome Allosaurus!
May I present...the amazing Allosaurus!

Today we welcome the one and only Allosaurus to have a talk, then we hunt with Cryolophosaurus, and then we compare roars with Tyrannosaurus Rex, and last, we have the first group meeting of the Spinosaurus show!
Welcome to todays Spinosaurus talk show!
All Theropods united!
Now, how do you hunt?
Hello Cryolophosaurus!
Interesting! Ok, now the next thing for today! May I welcome...the Cryolophosaurus!
You welcome! Now lets have the big Theropod group foto!
1st class! The loudest roar I have ever heard!
And you should be! Now, please give you loudest roar!
Very interesting! Now I welcome the Tyrannosaurus Rex!
It used to be meat but since I had tea with the Giganotosaurus, it's fruit salad!
Thanks for having me!
Well, I run after the thing I am hunting and then I invite it to tea and have a lovely afternoon!
Cool to be here!
I am honoured to take part in this show!
ROOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAARRRRRRRRRRR!!!!!!!!!!!
How was that?
Oh thank you!
